---
import MailFastIcon from "./icons/MailFast.astro";
---
<article class="relative rounded-3xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-x-4 py-6 px-4 shadow-xl shadow-white/5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700 via-gray-900 to-black overflow-hidden group">
    <aside class="md:w-2/3 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-balance mb-4">¿Qué esperas para llevar tus ideas o negocio al <span class="text-scooter-500">mundo digital</span>?</h2>
        <p class="text-balance text-base lg:text-lg"><span class="text-mango-300/90 font-semibold">¡Mándame un mail!</span> <span class=" opacity-75">Expresa tus ideas y estaré encantado de responderte.</span> <span class="text-mango-300 font-bold">Estas a un solo clic de dejar tu huella en internet</span>.</p>
    </aside>
    <a class="mt-4 md:mt-0 rounded-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-100/20
    relative z-10 overflow-hidden before:content-[''] before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:h-full before:w-0 before:rounded-xl before:bg-scooter-500 before:-z-10 before:transition-all before:duration-500 before:hover:w-full hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-scooter-500/50 ease duration-500 mx-auto" href="mailto:mmontoyaabadia@gmail.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Escribe ahora</a>
    <MailFastIcon class="hidden md:block size-64 text-neutral-500/10 absolute  top-0 right-0 group-hover:translate-x-16 transition-transform duration-700 -z-1"/>
</article>
